org.slieb.dependencies

Class DependencyResolver<D extends DependencyNode<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.slieb.dependencies.DependencyResolver<D>
  • Type Parameters:
    D - A extension of the dependency node.

    public class DependencyResolver<D extends DependencyNode<?>>
extends Object
    The dependency Resolver will resolve a collection of Dependencies. note: A draw back of this method is that too many items in the require chain will cause a long recursing and result in a stackoverflow.
